title.rendered: Health Camp at ME centre at Baikunthapur

content.rendered: A health camp held at the Smile Foundation’s Mission Education centre BTS at Baikunthapur in South 24 Parganas district, West Bengal benefitted more than 200 children. A qualified doctor, assisted by a pharmacist and teachers from the centres ensured that all the children were properly diagnosed, following which free medicines were also disbursed to the children.
